description: Kollect on Demand Holding AB engages in the provision of waste disposal services. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2019-12-19. The firm was founded in August 2019 and is located in Sweden. The company operates within two separate, but related, business areas: an online waste platform and waste drop-off containers. Within the platform segment, the Company operates an online marketplace that connects customers (business and domestic) who need to dispose of waste with waste companies who collect and recycle waste, using Kollects technology platform. The firm also operates BIGbin, which is a fully sealed compactor that the company installs on petrol forecourts or car parks for customers to drop off bags of domestic waste.
